name: Ryan WHEELER, Petitioner v. Honorable C. Darnell JONES, Respondent

parties: Ryan WHEELER, Petitioner v. Honorable C. Darnell JONES, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of September, 2008, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The judge’s name is to be stricken from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
